snippet.title: Friday:Death to Arthur Yahtzee Gameplay
snippet.description: The first game Ben 'Yahtzee' Croshaw ever released onto the internet. It's absoloute shit with the entertainment value of a butter knife vasectomy but everyone starts somewhere. Running in a windows 95 VM using Oracle VirtualBox
